Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: US defence of Israel
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0409pgn
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 4 Dec 1977
Middle East peace talks stumble over US's moral commitment to defend the state of Israel. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less